{"tid":2246434,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"K-POP最初零韓國血統的「黑人」女歌手正式出道！八頭身完美身材比例成焦點","createTime":"2020-10-17T05:20:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T17:39:10.000Z","uid":74065,"like":20,"dislike":210,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"9bf79680e4dcf13d6f8005ce8b4c230b21ead4ae","tid":2246434,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T05:20:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2020/10/17/550_1548673_1602866830.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2020%2F10%2F17%2F550_1548673_1602866830.webp&h=a77c8b1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n5人女子組合BLACKSWAN以《TONIGHT》在韓國歌謠界出道，黑人成員Fatou吸引了大家的視線。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2020/10/17/550_1548675_1602866783.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2020%2F10%2F17%2F550_1548675_1602866783.webp&h=71ca253f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n韓國時間10月16日下午6點，Danal Entertainment和各種音源網站上公開了BLACKSWAN的《TONIGHT》。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2020/10/17/550_1548676_1602866787.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2020%2F10%2F17%2F550_1548676_1602866787.webp&h=838f39f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBLACKSWAN是由Leia、Hyeme、Youngheun、Fatou、Judy組成的5人女子組合，是過去Rania的成員們再次出道的組合。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2020/10/17/550_1548677_1602866791.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2020%2F10%2F17%2F550_1548677_1602866791.webp&h=7a30100b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成員中最引人注目的是擔任主Rapper的1995年生比利時出身的Fatou。至今爲止，混血Rapper有很多，但是沒有韓國血統的黑人成員在K-POP中還是首次。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2020/10/17/550_1548678_1602866794.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2020%2F10%2F17%2F550_1548678_1602866794.webp&h=4c382565&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據悉，Fatou身高173cm，出道前曾作爲模特活動。公開的照片中，她不僅擁有完美比例的8頭身身材，而且五官端正，散發着與眾不同的魅力。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2020/10/17/550_1548679_1602867029.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2020%2F10%2F17%2F550_1548679_1602867029.webp&h=926e5b6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n出生在塞內加爾、生活在比利時的她，在出道前雖然不熟練，但是用工工整整的字跡給粉絲們留下了用韓文寫的信。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1.wishnote.tw/550/2020/10/17/550_1548674_1602866779.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.wishnote.tw%2F550%2F2020%2F10%2F17%2F550_1548674_1602866779.webp&h=7088cf6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另外，BLACKSWAN於7月7日被委任爲韓國平昌郡宣傳大使等，已經通過多種多樣的自由出道宣傳活動確保了衆多粉絲。"},{"pid":"09e514fca29053708b62540dc51a4b8a1b563055","tid":2246434,"uid":205928,"like":314,"dislike":9,"score":305,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T05:22:08.000Z","msg":"係靚但唔係幾岩做kstar"},{"pid":"3ed48de474e711a787ffc63529f64e6b5ec8d3aa","tid":2246434,"uid":143093,"like":149,"dislike":18,"score":131,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T05:22:11.000Z","msg":"是但搵個nigga吹奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"117b18f6ea19ba55c93c11a950537271699fa843","tid":2246434,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T05:22:16.000Z","msg":"幾正"},{"pid":"2cc367e1e58b69c9ad601a125c0ca2f59fd04449","tid":2246434,"uid":99700,"like":3,"dislike":25,"score":-22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T05:23:24.000Z","msg":"想屌佢隻鮑魚"},{"pid":"e6526abdbf8500bf88dbb89ebefcd8844ac7816b","tid":2246434,"uid":363119,"like":36,"dislike":8,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T05:23:55.000Z","msg":"NIGGA LIVES MATTER<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"230cedcbb8d1e2f7f207624815a075e5541a8774","tid":2246434,"uid":74065,"like":164,"dislike":0,"score":164,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T05:25:36.000Z","msg":"哩D黑人參加偶運實拎牌"},{"pid":"ff7cf4640ad40f3bb4edbaffeb7d6e023e747227","tid":2246434,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0